tructure_readme_md_support_layout_analysis_and_table_recognition_one_key_to_export_chart_images_to_excel_files", "label": "2021.8.3 released PaddleOCR v2.2, add a new structured documents analysis toolkit, i.e., [PP-Structure](https://github.com/PaddlePaddle/PaddleOCR/blob/release/2.2/ppstructure/README.md), support layout analysis and table recognition (One-key to export chart images to Excel files)", "file_type": "document", "source_file": "docs/update/update.en.md", "source_location": "L196"}, {"id": "c_users_pntha_onedrive_documents_antigravity_thevocr_vietocr_docs_update_update_en_2021_4_8_release_end_to_end_text_recognition_algorithm_pgnet_https_cdn_aaai_org_ojs_16383_16383_13_19877_1_2_20210518_pdf_which_is_published_in_aaai_2021_find_tutorial_here_https_github_com_paddlepaddle_paddleocr_blob_release_2_1_doc_doc_en_pgnet_en_md_release_multi_language_recognition_models_https_github_com_paddlepaddle_paddleocr_blob_release_2_1_doc_doc_en_multi_languages_en_md_support_more_than_80_languages_recognition_especially_the_performance_of_english_recognition_model_version3_x_model_list_md_is_optimized", "label": "2021.4.8 release end-to-end text recognition algorithm [PGNet](https://cdn.aaai.org/ojs/16383/16383-13-19877-1-2-20210518.pdf) which is published in AAAI 2021. Find tutorial [here](https://github.com/PaddlePaddle/PaddleOCR/blob/release/2.1/doc/doc_en/pgnet_en.md)\uff1brelease multi language recognition [models](https://github.com/PaddlePaddle/PaddleOCR/blob/release/2.1/doc/doc_en/multi_languages_en.md), support more than 80 languages recognition; especially, the performance of [English recognition model](../version3.x/model_list.md) is Optimized", "file_type": "document", "source_file": "docs/update/update.en.md", "source_location": "L198"}, {"id": "c_users_pntha_onedrive_documents_antigravity_thevocr_vietocr_docs_update_update_en_2021_1_21_update_more_than_25_multilingual_recognition_models_models_list_version2_x_ppocr_model_list_en_md_including_english_chinese_german_french_japanese_spanish_portuguese_russia_arabic_and_so_on_models_for_more_languages_will_continue_to_be_updated_develop_plan_https_github_com_paddlepaddle_paddleocr_issues_1048", "label": "2021.1.21 update more than 25+ multilingual recognition models [models list](../version2.x/ppocr/model_list.en.md), including\uff1aEnglish, Chinese, German, French, Japanese\uff0cSpanish\uff0cPortuguese Russia Arabic and so on.  Models for more languages will continue to be updated [Develop Plan](https://github.com/PaddlePaddle/PaddleOCR/issues/1048)", "file_type": "document", "source_file": "docs/update/update.en.md", "source_location": "L200"}, {"id": "c_users_pntha_onedrive_documents_antigravity_thevocr_vietocr_docs_update_update_en_2020_12_15_update_data_synthesis_tool_i_e_style_text_https_github_com_pfcclab_styletext_blob_main_readme_md_easy_to_synthesize_a_large_number_of_images_which_are_similar_to_the_target_scene_image", "label": "2020.12.15 update Data synthesis tool, i.e., [Style-Text](https://github.com/PFCCLab/StyleText/blob/main/README.md)\uff0ceasy to synthesize a large number of images which are similar to the target scene image", "file_type": "document", "source_file": "docs/update/update.en.md", "source_location": "L202"}, {"id": "c_users_pntha_onedrive_documents_antigravity_thevocr_vietocr_docs_update_update_en_2020_11_25_update_a_new_data_annotation_tool_i_e_ppocrlabel_https_github_com_pfcclab_ppocrlabel_blob_main_readme_md_which_is_helpful_to_improve_the_labeling_efficiency_moreover_the_labeling_results_can_be_used_in_training_of_the_pp_ocr_system_directly", "label": "2020.11.25 Update a new data annotation tool, i.e., [PPOCRLabel](https://github.com/PFCCLab/PPOCRLabel/blob/main/README.md), which is helpful to improve the labeling efficiency. Moreover, the labeling results can be used in training of the PP-OCR system directly", "file_type": "document", "source_file": "docs/update/update.en.md", "source_location": "L204"}, {"id": "c_users_pntha_onedri